# gitignore contributors: scroll down to GitHub and 10000+ others

## Build results
build/
DerivedData/

## Project settings
xcuserdata/

## Schemes
#
# Often it is a good idea to check in the user's schemes, however
# if you want to keep them local, then uncomment the following line.
# xcshareddata/xcschemes

## Xcode 8+
#
# If you are using Xcode 8 or later, you might want to uncomment the
# following lines to ignore the new .xccheckout files.
# *.xccheckout

## Swift Package Manager
#
# Add this line if you want to ignore the folder where Swift Packages are stored.
# .build/

## CocoaPods
#
# We recommend against adding the Pods directory to your repository.
# However, if you'd like to include it, comment out the following line.
Pods/
*.xcworkspace

## Carthage
#
# We recommend against adding the Carthage directory to your repository.
# However, if you'd like to include it, comment out the following line.
Carthage/Build/

## AccuRev
.accurev/

## Fastlane
#
# It is recommended to not store the fastlane/report.xml file in git
# fastlane/report.xml

## App Store Connect
#
# If you use fastlane to upload screenshots, they will be stored in this directory.
# fastlane/screenshots

